Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}(喜欢)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 班里养的兔子死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吃了什么不好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们干的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天看到三个女生聚在兔笼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 是小梅…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小梅说它什么都吃 要给它吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不要 但她非要给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(橘)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什么也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 为什么这样对我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 软糖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.27,0:01:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 不要开着龙头打洗发水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了风铃 有夏天的感觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 挂得晚了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候都不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么事都是只要开始了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌词啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也要吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心点儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 那个阴暗女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你多少年没有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装没听见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要问些失礼的问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是十六年都没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友也十六年没交过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后估计还会一年年持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能称为朋友的人 至今为止倒是有过几个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我已经发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有朋友 也只会伤害到自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 昨天那种情况真是太气人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说清野的女生都是巨乳 还很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才那么兴奋赶过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果女生都是冲着大和来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种好像不关你事儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最可爱的那个女孩儿绝对盯上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别小看我中西的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你和那女孩儿互留手机号了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 咋回事 why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么为什么呀 只是初次见面又不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么可爱的女孩儿向你发出那么热情的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我觉得和其他女孩子没什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校最受欢迎的男人就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家憧憬的 又对大家亲切的黑泽大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在讽刺我么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子在你眼里不会全部都一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没觉得她们有优劣之分…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天晚上去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你打电话你没接呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和清野高中的人一起吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种场合怎么不叫上麻美一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次一定告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 下次大家一起去K歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呢 这个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连麻美 都想要从我这里夺走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美她可是我的真命天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是胸部太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是只看胸部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有只喜欢胸部 麻美她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和我是同班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来都那副样子 不说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概没人听过她的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种人最没招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早操究竟为什么而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 你们两个…景色很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态中西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要遮就别穿这么短的裙子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别欺负人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在提醒她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一遮呢 反倒会引起别人的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是你在邀请人看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟色老头似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天和清野的女生一起吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是联谊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 吃个饭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾 也和我们一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 很少见的及膝裙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了和别人不同 引人注意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这种裙子的会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 什么呀 是橘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 中西 你干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次 都说不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别狡辩了 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是中西做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把脑袋摔坏了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘…梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去社团啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 什么态度呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己多了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\frz12.278\pos(962,155)\3c&HDAE8F7&\4c&HDAE8F7&\c&H59616A&}踢无辜的人太可恶了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\frz12.278\4c&HDAE8F7&\c&H59616A&\pos(1139,629)\3c&HB7C1CE&}去道歉！笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘梅同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉？为什么你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是我朋友做错了事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉你裙子的那个人叫中西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是和你一个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 反正我们也没有在班里讲过话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙虽然很嚣张 但是没什么恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是会让人讨厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我踢错了人真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不过你的态度一下子转变得那么快…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得橘同学很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:10:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是觉得捉弄我很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到橘同学是我喜欢的那种有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所说的有趣是指… 要怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得太多会坏肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来交换电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的交换电话是指交换邮箱 不是手机本身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你踢飞的时候 你的手受伤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的伤只用这么小的创可贴治愈不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要的话就和我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样了 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被讨厌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久都没和学校的人讲话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给了我手机号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是拥有那样微笑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也不会给他打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力酥皮饼出锅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚出炉的巧克力酥皮饼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是发烧了吧 脸这么红
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸才没红 也没有发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这些东西 请算账
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食也都放在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请分开放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 可以的话 请根据个数来包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收您2000日元 找零950日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没算错 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅 来帮我弄一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 「我回来了」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想这些有的没的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正到头来还是会被背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说梅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有给我打电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一直在等你电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说过要给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就联系一下下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说讨厌跟朋友聊天什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我家和打工的地方的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总是会轻易地背叛别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校这地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「必须把某个人当靶子耍的混蛋集结地」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像过家家似的 装作关系很好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦情况不对 就会置身事外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想跟那样的人成朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是所有人都那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友这种东西 对我来说不是必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到大和了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.25,0:16:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿去唱K吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去没事吗 只限萌妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中西你真是的 总是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群女孩子不是会热闹点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这种烂借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我只要有小麻美就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉呢 弄到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 是面包店的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道从面包店到这里的回家路线恰巧跟我相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 从刚刚开始就一直在那里站着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还往我这看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是碰巧 是跟踪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先接个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁打的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我是橘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点梅 你现在在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三丁目的便利店里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来 待在那里别走开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的那个男的 是我打工的地方的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天关门了之后就跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟了多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多35分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是跟踪狂么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也联系不上 能商量的人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰激凌？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑过来的 热死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的我都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道这是什么样的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的初…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:50.95,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(976,429)}「接吻」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么没了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:13.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\be3}慣れきた表情の　冷たい朝が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:13.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}喜欢能看到你熟悉表情的清冷早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:19.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}あからさまなった意図みせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:19.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}如此直率地向我表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}予言のような空の色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}天空的颜色如预言般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:31.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}そんなに意地悪しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:31.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}不要这样的捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:36.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}笑った薄い唇に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:36.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}你的薄唇边挂着微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}傾く影を追いかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}我追寻着你倾斜的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:48.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}君さえもわからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:48.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}即使我还对你一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:57.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}頼りない　もっと抱きしめて放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:57.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}虽然不可靠 但请自由地拥抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}重ねていくいつもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:00.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}总会有许多的交汇处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:08.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}頼りないぐらい　不器用なslow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:08.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}虽然不可靠 笨拙的slow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:14.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}揺れる気持ちを乗るの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:14.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}但还是希望你能跟着摇曳的心一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了 就是一个起点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这就是「只要你说你爱我」崭新的开篇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间的话 就请把标题读成「爱我」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这省略有些牵强啊
